{"tid":1420214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深圳公安演練　逾千警力防暴槍驅散穿黑衣戴頭盔示威者","createTime":"2019-08-06T04:04:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T04:39:08.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b8b1d45c0219593a5e67ff52679a00bd3f3fbb66","tid":1420214,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:04:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1472999_1_20190806112645.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1472999_1_20190806112645.jpg&h=6ebf24b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n深圳市公安局早上10時半，在寶安區海濱廣場舉行夏季練兵，模擬特警演練和應急處置突發事件。<br />\n<br />\n行動名為「深圳亮劍」， 模擬出動1500人警力，面對2000名示威者的場面。深圳市公安局在官方微博直播，大批特警人員一字排開，手持長盾牌組成多個分隊，應對身穿黑色衣服、戴上頭盔、口罩，以及手持標語的示威者，現場廣播起初形容他們為滋事分子。<br />\n<br />\n示威者隨後衝擊不斷升級，他們高叫口號，用磚頭、木棒、鐵馬和火燒手推車，衝擊特警的防線，又掟「汽油彈」，現場廣播改為形容示威者是暴徒。特警其後向天施放催淚煙和防暴槍，驅散示威者， 並拘捕部分人，成功處置暴力騷亂事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1472999-20190806.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1472999-20190806.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=NNqT6wnuCkALqD5scUUSnHGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=95f9f1ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1472999-20190806.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fd97c15a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1472999-20190806.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"16e6addf49f28f30ea9b70a3df5dd7f340b9dcaf","tid":1420214,"uid":109780,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:05:28.000Z","msg":"有樣嘢佢哋模擬唔到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">智商</span></span>"},{"pid":"598e83deeb96112777a52e059aff7b19706a6123","tid":1420214,"uid":22590,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:06:34.000Z","msg":"如何打飛機.JPG"},{"pid":"1065762146b1307db802d61af9cc23c10